<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Order is Confirmed! (And a Special Offer For Next Time)</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Your Order is Confirmed!</h1>
        <p>Hi <%= customerName %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your recent purchase at Brands Discounts! Your order #<%= orderNumber %> is confirmed.</p>
        <p>We noticed you didn't use our exclusive $10 first item offer this time. We’d love for you to enjoy this deal on your next order! Remember, when you spend $60 or more, you can get <strong>any item for just $10</strong> – and you’ll be automatically enrolled in our loyalty program.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out.</p>
        <p>Warm regards,<br/>The Brands Discounts Team</p>
        <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@brandsdiscounts.com">hello@brandsdiscounts.com</a></p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Brands Discounts. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
